HEADWORD: minelaying
<hw>minelaying</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act or process of laying
explosive mines in concealed places to destroy enemy personnel and
equipment.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> mining.</syn>⟦br⟧
